 in investments in turnaround restructuring stressed credit liquidation litigation equity and curvecapital structure arbitrage buyout and distressed situations it invests in senior and subordinated secured and unsecured debt and equity in both public and private companies the firm invests in communication equipment and diversified financial services it seeks to make controlling investments in its portfolio companies and also seeks minority investments matlinpatterson global advisers llc was founded in  and is based in new york new york with additional offices in london united kingdom são paulo bra matlinpatterson global advisers llc is a private equity firm specializing in investments in turnaround restructuring stressed credit liquidation litigation equity and curvecapital structure arbitrage buyout and distressed situations it invests in senior and subordinated secured and unsecured debt and equity in both public and private companies the firm invests in communication equipment and diversified financial services it seeks to make controlling investments in its portfolio companies and also seeks minority investments matlinpatterson global advisers llc was founded in  and is based in new york new york with additional offices in london united kingdom são paulo brasil hyderabad india and central hong kong detailed description  madison avenueth floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwmatlinpattersoncom key executives for matlinpatterson global advisers llc mr david j matlin jd cofounder and chief executive officer age  mr marc rosenthal coportfolio manager and cochief executive officer ms noelle savarese coportfolio manager and cochief executive officer mr mark r patterson cofounder and chairman age  ms sherry gao cpa chief financial officer compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc